ury sidelined him for the season and a 1-game suspension kept him out of the season opener.  Fitzgerald threw for 154 yards with two touchdowns and ran for another 159 yards.  Mississippi State compiled a total of 538 yards of total offense where Kansas State only managed 213.\n\nKansas State continued with its two-quarterback system, switching snaps between Skylar Thompson and Alex Delton. Kansas State running back Alex Barnes managed 75 yards rushing, but the Wildcats fell short to lose the game 31-10.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/college-football/recap?gameId=401012266|publisher=[[ESPN]]|title=Fitzgerald leads No. 18 Miss St to 31-10 rout of K-State|accessdate=September 16, 2018|date=September 15, 2018}}</ref>\n\n===Louisiana===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=Ragin' Cajuns\n|R1= 3\n|R2= 0\n|R3= 0\n|R4= 7\n|Home='''No. 16 Bulldogs'''\n|H1= 14\n|H2= 21\n|H3= 14\n|H4= 7\n}}\n{{see also|2018 Louisiana Ragin' Cajuns football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Mississippi State Bulldogs|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 3\u20130\n| September 5, 1987\n| '''W''' 31\u20133\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===at Kentucky===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=No. 14 Bulldogs\n|R1=0\n|R2=7\n|R3=0\n|R4=0\n|Home='''Wildcats'''\n|H1=0\n|H2=7\n|H3=7\n|H4=14\n}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n{{CollegeSecondaryHeader|team=Mississippi State Bulldogs|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 23\u201322\n| October 21, 2017\n| '''W''' 45\u20137\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===Florida===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road='''Gators'''\n|R1=0\n|R2=3\n|R3=7\n|R4=3\n|Home=No. 23 Bulldogs\n|H1=3\n|H2=3\n|H3=0\n|H4=0\n}}\n{{see also|2018 Florida Gators football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Mississippi State Bulldogs|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 19\u201333\u20132\n| October 16, 2010\n| '''W''' 10\u20137\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===Auburn===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=No. 8 Tigers\n|R1=3\n|R2=0\n|R3=3\n|R4=3\n|Home='''Bulldogs'''\n|H1=3\n|H2=10\n|H3=3\n|H4=7\n}}\n{{see also|2018 Auburn Tigers football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Mississippi State Bulldogs|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 26\u201363\u20133\n| September 30, 2017\n| '''L''' 10\u201349\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===at LSU===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=No. 22 Bulldogs\n|R1=3\n|R2=0\n|R3=0\n|R4=0\n|Home='''No. 5 Tigers'''\n|H1=7\n|H2=3\n|H3=6\n|H4=3\n}}\n{{see also|2018 LSU Tigers football team|LSU\u2013Mississippi State football rivalry}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n{{CollegeSecondaryHeader|team=Mississippi State Bulldogs|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 35\u201373\u20133\n| September 16, 2017\n| '''W''' 37\u20137\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===Texas A&M===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=No. 16 Aggies\n|R1=0\n|R2=10\n|R3=3\n|R4=0\n|Home='''Bulldogs'''\n|H1=7\n|H2=0\n|H3=7\n|H4=14\n}}\n{{see also|2018 Texas A&M Aggies football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Mississippi State Bulldogs|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 6\u20135\n| October 28, 2017\n| '''W''' 35\u201314\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===Louisiana Tech===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=LT Bulldogs\n|R1=3\n|R2=0\n|R3=0\n|R4=0\n|Home='''No. 21 MSU Bulldogs'''\n|H1=21\n|H2=10\n|H3=7\n|H4=7\n}}\n{{see also|2018 Louisiana Tech Bulldogs football team}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Mississippi State Bulldogs|Overall record|Last meeting|Result}}\n|- align=\"center\"\n| 10\u20133\n| September 9, 2017\n| '''W''' 57\u201321\n|}\n{{-}}\n\n===at Alabama===\n{{Linescore Amfootball|\n|Road=No. 18 Bulldogs\n|R1=0\n|R2=0\n|R3=0\n|R4=0\n|Home='''No. 1 Crimson Tide'''\n|H1=14\n|H2=7\n|H3=0\n|H4=3\n}}\n{{see also|2018 Alabama Crimson Tide football team|Alabama\u2013Mississippi State fo