a|South American Champions]]\n | years = [[1919 South American Championship|1919]] (First title)\n | after = [[1920 South American Championship|1920]] {{fb-rt|URU}}\n}}\n{{succession box\n | before = [[1921 South American Championship|1921]] {{fb-rt|ARG}}\n | title = [[Copa Am\u00e9rica|South American Champions]]\n | years = [[1922 South American Championship|1922]] (Second title)\n | after = [[1923 South American Championship|1923]] {{fb-rt|URU}}\n}}\n{{succession box\n | before = [[1947 South American Championship|1947]] {{fb-rt|ARG}}\n | title = [[Copa Am\u00e9rica|South American Champions]]\n | years = [[1949 South American Championship|1949]] (Third title)\n | after = [[1953 South American Championship|1953]] {{fb-rt|PAR|1842}}\n}}\n{{succession box\n | before = [[1987 Copa Am\u00e9rica|1987]] {{fb-rt|URU}}\n | title = [[Copa Am\u00e9rica|South American Champions]]\n | years = [[1989 Copa Am\u00e9rica|1989]] (Fourth title)\n | after = [[1991 Copa Am\u00e9rica|1991]] {{fb-rt|ARG}}\n}}\n{{succession box\n | before = [[1995 Copa Am\u00e9rica|1995]] {{fb-rt|URU}}\n | title = [[Copa Am\u00e9rica|South American Champions]]\n | years = [[1997 Copa Am\u00e9rica|1997]] (Fifth title)<br />[[1999 Copa Am\u00e9rica|1999]] (Sixth title)\n | after = [[2001 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2001]] {{fb-rt|COL}}\n}}\n{{succession box\n | before = [[2001 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2001]] {{fb-rt|COL}}\n | title = [[Copa Am\u00e9rica|South American Champions]]\n | years = [[2004 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2004]] (Seventh title)<br />[[2007 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2007]] (Eighth title)\n | after = [[2011 Copa Am\u00e9rica|2011]] {{fb-rt|URU}}\n}}\n{{S-ach|aw}}\n{{succession box\n | before = {{fb-rt|GER}}<br /> {{fb-rt|HON}}\n | after = {{fb-rt|NED}}<br /> {{fb-rt|ARG}}\n | title = [[FIFA World Rankings#Team of the Year|FIFA Team of the Year]]\n | years = 1994\u20131999<br />2002\u20132006\n}}\n{{Succession box|before=[[Manuel Estiarte]]|title=[[Princess of Asturias Award#Sports (Deportes)|Prince of Asturias Award for S